  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/SaveUNousFRWorkplan_1.png?t=1727020806\" /></span><br>For Hell's Sake is a fast-paced 2D platform game where you play as a demon on a mission to break an old contract.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Constantly hunted by a superior entity, you will have to move forward. Use your fluid and fast movements to cross the world and avoid the traps it contains.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You are going to die. A lot. For sure. But fear not, the Underworld is still with you. Place limited portals wherever you want in order to reappear there in the event of a problem. Be careful not to overdo it and place them with discernment.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You are being hunted. DON'T GET CAUGHT. Or the portals of Hell will no longer be able to do anything for you..<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/0b6120a4ce1addc55a4338c488897c87.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An original checkpoint management mechanic</li><li>A challenging difficulty</li><li>Fluid and aerial movement</li><li>Four levels of difficulty</li><li>Several skins to unlock while playing</li><li>A leaderboard system personal </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/SaveUNousFRWorkplan_1.png?t=1727020806\" /></span><br>For Hell's Sake is a fast-paced 2D platform game where you play as a demon on a mission to break an old contract.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/1bd275957b7c878ee0403200aa95d1fb.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Constantly hunted by a superior entity, you will have to move forward. Use your fluid and fast movements to cross the world and avoid the traps it contains.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/a9e64030c035364f82e2b397d558069d.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You are going to die. A lot. For sure. But fear not, the Underworld is still with you. Place limited portals wherever you want in order to reappear there in the event of a problem. Be careful not to overdo it and place them with discernment.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.poster.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.webm?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/2ca34e0895aa8042d5106810b23bdea2.mp4?t=1727020806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You are being hunted. DON'T GET CAUGHT. Or the portals of Hell will no longer be able to do anything for you..<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2955850/extras/0b6120a4ce1addc55a4338c488897c87.avif?t=1727020806\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An original checkpoint management mechanic</li><li>A challenging difficulty</li><li>Fluid and aerial movement</li><li>Four levels of difficulty</li><li>Several skins to unlock while playing</li><li>A leaderboard system personal </li></ul>",
